  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to UDisks2</title>

    <para>
      The <application>UDisks2</application> package provides a daemon, 
      tools and libraries to access and manipulate disks and storage 
      devices.
    </para>

    &lfs70_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
